## Projects

- [Pixel Planet Today](https://www.pixelplanettoday.com): Social media snippets pairing environmental facts with pixel art designs.
- [Wasted Space](https://www.wastedspace.fun): A classic arcade game that drives home concepts of reusing and recycling.
- [Pinekeepers](https://www.pinekeepers.com): A retro-inspired game that turns trees saved in the digital world into real-life saplings.
- [Canapi](https://www.canapi.io): Automation software (marketplace and API) that turns digital interactions into environmental contributions.